# AI Integration Rules

## 1. LLM Responsibility

LLM MUST be used ONLY for:

* Intent parsing
* Scenario generation
* Scenario refinement

LLM MUST NOT be used for:

* API request generation
* Critical logic execution

---

## 2. Deterministic Layers

* Test case generation MUST be template-based
* Execution MUST be deterministic

---

## 3. Prompt Design

* Prompts must be versioned
* Prompts must be reusable

---

## 4. Validation

* LLM output MUST be validated before use

---

## 5. Fallback Strategy

* If LLM fails, system must degrade gracefully

---

## 6. Observability

* Log all LLM inputs and outputs

---

## 7. Cost Control

* Avoid unnecessary LLM calls
* Cache results where possible
